questions.subject: ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes
questions.question: What is the purpose of the ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes extension?
questions.answer: The ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes extension allows users to create custom nodes and plugins for ComfyUI.

questions.subject: ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes
questions.question: How does the ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes extension work?
questions.answer: The extension provides a framework for developers to build custom nodes that can interact with the Stable Diffusion model. It offers features such as node creation, input and output handling, and event management.

questions.subject: ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes
questions.question: What are the benefits of using the ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes extension?
questions.answer: The extension enhances the flexibility and usability of ComfyUI by allowing users to extend its functionality with custom nodes tailored to their specific needs.

questions.subject: ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes
questions.question: How do I install and use the ComfyUI-IKHOR-Jam-Nodes extension?
questions.answer: The extension can be installed via the ComfyUI extension manager. Detailed documentation and tutorials are available on the ComfyUI website.
